        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "For compatibility reasons with mail clients the headers of a mime part should be\r\n\r\nContent-Type: application\/pdf; name=\"file.pdf\"\r\nContent-Transfer-Encoding: base64\r\nContent-Disposition: attachment; filename=\"file.pdf\"\r\n\r\ninstead of\r\n\r\nContent-Type: application\/pdf;\r\nContent-Transfer-Encoding: base64\r\nContent-Disposition: attachment; filename=\"file.pdf\"\r\n\r\nOtherwise some mail clients wouldn't recognize the filename correctly.\r\nShould be fixed in Zend_Mime_Part getHeadersArray"
        },
